We told them that we were
going to go up to this place

00:30:21.120 --> 00:30:22.703
where there's this
giant thing of DNA.

00:30:22.703 --> 00:30:24.840
And, like, we had photos
from the lab the next day.

00:30:24.840 --> 00:30:26.670
And they were on Amazon
within 10 minutes,

00:30:26.670 --> 00:30:29.950
and they had, like, next-day
